description: People who have important information should better not step on unknown territory. But some men seem to be in need of a thrill. A certain Mr. Rene was such a candidate. The Baroness had found out that Mr. Rene, who is one of Mr. Kayne's tax counselors, was looking for kinky sexual adventures on online dating websites. And she is his new match! A sexual adventure - that was exactly what he should get. The Baroness starts the game with some intense mummification. At her complete mercy, Mr. Rene has to participate in kinky food play, sploshing, and spitting. But soon his sexy date gets more serious. The Baroness wants his information, and torments her victim with flogging and intense CBT.
title: Ep 9 - Kinky Blind Date: Mummified by Baroness Davina Dust
